## Who is this user guide for?
This user guide is for the teams who are using the Minsitry of Justice Cloud platform or 
wanted to deploy and manage containerized applications 
on the cloud platform. The platform manages the infrastructure	
that your application runs on and provides tooling for teams to deploy and	
manage their applications on that infrastructure.

